HomeTitle.h1: Build and ship AI models on a single, collaborative platform
HomeTitle.span: GitData.AI is your one-stop-shop MLOps platform to accelerate your service with AI and Data Science. Simply put, with GitData.AI you can go from idea to production in minutes instead of months. All while resting assured that there is complete traceability and reproducibility over time.

HomeFT.TS: GitData.AI is an open-source team to build cost-effective at scale MLOps platform which enable data engineering teams to automate complex pipelines with sophisticated data transformations deeply intertwined with the data itself.
HomeFT.C1R1: Complex data environments in the Modern Enterprise
HomeFT.C1R1Desc: Enable AI/ML to be effectively deployed in the context of complex data environments with varied goals and missions
HomeFT.C1R2: Value creation and continual improvement for the Digital transformation
HomeFT.C1R2Desc: Enable an organization to actually use AI/ML models as part of a data ecosystem of value creation and continual improvement.
HomeFT.C1R3: Keep AI responsible, accountable, and oriented towards humans.
HomeFT.C1R3Desc: Enable a more responsible deployment of AI/ML: Ensure Auditability, Explainability, and Interpretability.
HomeFT.C2R1: Enable a more responsible deployment of AI/ML: Ensure Auditability, Explainability, and Interpretability.
HomeFT.C2R1Desc: Utilize data to drive the development and improvement of machine learning models.
HomeFT.C2R2Desc: Take an AI/ML model from development to an operational context.
HomeFT.C2R3Desc: Enable customers to use AI/ML solutions for their most critical problems.

HomePartOne.TS: GitData.AI focuses on building an AI operating system that allows an organization to effectively use AI/ML models as part of an ecosystem of value creation and continual improvement. In this way, GitData.AI's approach & goal helps encourage a more responsible deployment of AI/ML, or what is often referred to as “Responsible AI”.
